OL,3,CBusinesses set to lose #110m as
OL,4,Cvisitor numbers fall in Somerset
OL,6,FExperts are warning the economic
OL,7,Fchallenges faced by businesses in
OL,8,FSomerset are causing significant
OL,9,Fproblems for the tourism industry in
OL,10,Fthe county.
OL,12,FFigures from Visit Somerset show a 10%
OL,13,Fdecline in visitor numbers this summer
OL,14,Fcompared to the last.
OL,16,FAccording to tourism experts, this
OL,17,Floss in revenue to businesses like
OL,18,FB&Bs and hotels amounts to #110
OL,19,Fmillion.
