OL,3,CBusinesses set to lose #110m as
OL,4,Cvisitor numbers fall in Somerset
OL,6,FChief Executive of Visit Somerset John
OL,7,FTurner has raised concerns over the
OL,8,Fimpact of increases in the living wage
OL,9,Fand employers' national insurance.
OL,11,FHe said: "Some of the figures that I'm
OL,12,Fhearing about from some of our larger
OL,13,Fattractions are eye-watering.
OL,15,F"And where they were making small
OL,16,Fprofits, it has just been wiped off
OL,17,Fthe slate, completely wiped off the
OL,18,Fslate.
