OL,3,CBusinesses set to lose #110m as
OL,4,Cvisitor numbers fall in Somerset
OL,6,F"Some of our larger businesses employ
OL,7,Fthousands of staff, and you're talking
OL,8,Fhundreds and hundreds of thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds they've just had to find out of
OL,10,Fnowhere."
OL,12,FHaving opened just three months ago,
OL,13,Fthe team at Niche in Wells is
OL,14,Fdetermined to succeed but is facing
OL,15,Fannual business rates of just under
OL,16,F#20,000.
OL,18,FCo-owner Susan Ali said: "When you
OL,19,Fcompare what it was before, we're
OL,20,Fpaying double what everybody else was
OL,21,Fpaying."
