OL,3,CBusinesses set to lose #110m as
OL,4,Cvisitor numbers fall in Somerset
OL,6,FNearby, The Swan Inn is dealing with
OL,7,Fweekly expenditure running to #20,000
OL,8,Fpounds.
OL,10,FGeneral Manager Gordon Harby said:
OL,11,F"National insurance - the hike this
OL,12,Fyear has made a massive increase into
OL,13,Four wage costs.
OL,15,F"The rising cost of food, liquor...
OL,16,FEverything is having that huge impact
OL,17,Fon the business."
