OL,3,CBusinesses set to lose #110m as
OL,4,Cvisitor numbers fall in Somerset
OL,6,FOver at Wells Cathedral, visitor
OL,7,Fnumbers are up 15% compared to last
OL,8,Fyear but costs are increasing for the
OL,9,Fcustodians, with VAT now paid on
OL,10,Frepairs and renovations.
OL,12,FChief Operation Officer Nerys Watts
OL,13,Fexplained: "It costs over eight
OL,14,Fthousand pounds a day to keep the
OL,15,Fcathedral open."
